Regions and provinces in Italy (high detail, CC-BY Istat)

ll_get_nuts_it.Rd

2019 / WGS84 UTM32N

ll_get_nuts_it(
  name = NULL,
  level = 2,
  year = 2019,
  resolution = "low",
  silent = FALSE
)

Arguments

level

Defaults to "2", i.e. regioni. Available: "3" (i.e. province), and "lau", local administrative units.

Value

Examples

ll_set_folder("~/R/")
